description:
This is a 19 minute workout called '15 min DAILY STRETCH ROUTINE (Full Body Stretch for Flexibility & Mobility)' from the channel MadFit.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a quick, full body stretch you can add into your daily routines! Perfect to do first thing in the morning, before bed, or after a workout. Stretching is so important, so I've designed this daily routine for you to help with mobility and flexibility!
